OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784625517
OL,3,CLorry stuck under railway bridge
OL,4,Ccauses disruption
OL,6,FA lorry became wedged underneath a
OL,7,Frailway bridge in Oxfordshire on
OL,8,FMonday morning, closing a road for
OL,9,Fseveral hours.
OL,11,FPolice officers and Network Rail crews
OL,12,Fwere called to the A4129 near Princes
OL,13,FRisborough just after 8am, where a
OL,14,FDunelm lorry had become stuck.
OL,16,FEngineers were also called to the site
OL,17,Fin order to carry out a full safety
OL,18,Finspection.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
