PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784625517
OL,3,CLorry stuck under railway bridge
OL,4,Ccauses disruption
OL,6,FThe railway has remained open but
OL,7,Ftrains are crossing the bridge at a
OL,8,Fslower speed.
OL,10,FA spokesman for Network Rail said:
OL,11,F"Bridge strikes cause unnecessary
OL,12,Fdelays to passengers and motorists and
OL,13,Fare easily avoidable.
OL,15,F"There is no excuse for lorries
OL,16,Fhitting bridges, which are clearly
OL,17,Fmarked with height restrictions and
OL,18,Fwarning signs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784625517
OL,3,CLorry stuck under railway bridge
OL,4,Ccauses disruption
OL,6,F"It is always the driver's
OL,7,Fresponsibility to know the height of
OL,8,Ftheir vehicle and plan their journeys,
OL,9,Fnot relying on sat navs or map apps
OL,10,Fwhich might not be up-to-date.
OL,12,F"As part of our 'wise up and size up'
OL,13,Fcampaign, we urge drivers to carefully
OL,14,Fplan their routes and know their
OL,15,Fvehicle's restrictions to avoid bridge
OL,16,Fstrikes and help keep rail passengers
OL,17,Fand motorists on the move."
OL,19,FA representative for Dunelm said: "We
OL,20,Fare aware of an incident involving a
OL,21,FDunelm delivery vehicle this morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784625517
OL,3,CLorry stuck under railway bridge
OL,4,Ccauses disruption
OL,6,F"We recognise the disruption this
OL,7,Fincident has caused to local residents
OL,8,Fand those travelling through the area,
OL,9,Fand we apologise for any
OL,10,Finconveniences caused.
OL,12,F"As the facts are still being
OL,13,Festablished, it would not be
OL,14,Fappropriate to comment further at this
OL,15,Ftime."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
